<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #007bff; color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; }
        .content { padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; margin-top: 20px; }
        .original-message { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #007bff; }
        .reply-message { background: #e7f3ff; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #28a745; }
        .label { font-weight: bold; color: #555; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>ðŸ“§ Reply to Your Message</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hi <strong><%= clientName %></strong>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for reaching out. Here's the response to your inquiry:</p>
            
            <div class="original-message">
                <p class="label">Your Original Message:</p>
                <p><strong>Subject:</strong> <%= originalSubject %></p>
                <p><strong>Message:</strong><br><%= originalMessage %></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="reply-message">
                <p class="label">Our Reply:</p>
                <p><%= replyText %></p>
                <p><strong>From:</strong> <%= repliedBy %></p>
            </div>
            
            <p>If you have any further questions, feel free to reply to this email.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br><strong>Our Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>